Can we get ad credit for sweepstakes testing

Sweepstakes are generally not allowed, I recommend checking out our policy document for detailed guidelines on sweepstakes. You can find it here: Sweepstakes Policy. Let me know if you have any other questions!

For lead generation, ad credit functionality is not available for newly created accounts by default. To become eligible, the account must complete and pass business verification, accumulate over $5,000 in spend, and establish a relationship with an Account Manager who can request the ad credit functionality to be enabled for you.
